{
  "texts": [
    "By promoting critical thinking and media literacy, individuals can be better equipped to identify fake medical content and make informed decisions about their health.",
    "While LLMs have the potential to transform the content generation of medical data, their misuse for generating fake medical content raises significant ethical concerns.",
    "The development of advanced tools to detect and prevent the spread of fake medical content, along with increased awareness and",
    "10.3389/fradi.2023.1224682 education, can help mitigate the risks associated with the use of LLMs in medical content generation.",
    "The potential misuse of ChatGPT and similar AGI models in medical education raises significant ethical concerns."
  ]
}